        ## Test
        
        ```
        docker run --rm -p 88:88 ksauzz/docker-krb5:0.0.1
        pip install -r requirements-test.txt -r requirements.txt
        KRB5_CONFIG=tests/conf/krb5.conf.local pytest
        ```
        
